{"tid":2147091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 23歲ptu 狗初步確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-08-09T04:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:47:26.000Z","uid":319764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3aeca72c0ceccbed57f831db6b4397ef3c7a0520","tid":2147091,"uid":319764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"本港第三波武漢肺炎疫情似有回落之勢，短短一個早上又再多4名長者病逝，當中包括一人是屯門康和護老中心院友（第2955號個案）。康和護老中心至今已有7人離逝，本港死亡數字則增至51人；另一名駐守機動部隊的23歲男警初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，該名初步確診男警於昨日（8日）自行前往指定診所接受病毒檢測，之後接獲通知指其檢測結果呈陽性反應。該名男警正在接受機動部隊訓練，工作時沒有與公眾接觸，過去14日亦沒有外遊記錄，他最後一日上班日為8月7日。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示高度關注事件，並已指示與該男警可能有緊密接觸的警務人員，均獲安排在家工作及病毒檢測；警方亦已安排人員清潔及消毒警員接受訓練的基地；提醒警員注意個人衞生，減少社交接觸，減低傳染風險。"},{"pid":"b093fc8a628f38d8aedd832dc6fafb10b01f2937","tid":2147091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/RM23Y6NQ44ZLG4F4XJTVZ43URA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FRM23Y6NQ44ZLG4F4XJTVZ43URA%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c500e16e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FRM23Y6NQ44ZLG4F4XJTVZ43URA%2F&h=1874b69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/RM23Y6NQ44ZLG4F4XJTVZ43URA/</a>"},{"pid":"4ed5806b6be2552fe2979694613441aaaa21989b","tid":2147091,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"香檳各區冇貨"},{"pid":"7eab9de51d38d46aa67a295c84255063229d5a43","tid":2147091,"uid":306413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"連登jai: 三萬隻唔該"},{"pid":"55714d7ebf41d78478be949c46da686b316cc22b","tid":2147091,"uid":358652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐"}]}